---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="关于">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12 reveal">
        <span class="text-4xl font-serif text-primary">华</span>
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-medium">关于</h1>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-50 mt-1">About</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <p>你好，我是李华。一名热爱技术的开发者。</p>
        <p>这个博客是我的技术笔记本，记录学习过程中的思考与沉淀。</p>
        <h2>技术栈</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Astro — 静态站点生成器</li>
          <li>Tailwind CSS + daisyUI — 样式框架</li>
          <li>TypeScript — 类型安全</li>
          <li>MDX — 内容管理</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>联系</h2>
        <p>欢迎通过 Telegram 或者邮件与我交流。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  import "../scripts/scroll-reveal";
</script>
